20:43.801 --> 20:45.801
You bet.

20:47.634 --> 20:49.934
Now, now, boys,
this is a reunion.

20:49.934 --> 20:52.767
No need to pick up
exactly where we left off.

20:52.767 --> 20:54.133
If we did that,

20:54.133 --> 20:55.534
Connie would be
in the coat room

20:55.534 --> 20:56.601
with the band.

20:59.300 --> 21:01.834
Peggy,
did you hear the good news?

21:01.834 --> 21:03.667
I'm going to be reunion queen.

21:03.667 --> 21:05.534
Care to be my hag-in-waiting?

21:05.534 --> 21:08.434
Oh, no. You're wrong.

21:08.434 --> 21:10.434
Much as you're wrong

21:10.434 --> 21:12.467
in thinking that
women don't need deodorant.

21:14.267 --> 21:18.801
You see, I'm going
to be reunion queen.

21:18.801 --> 21:20.033
Check your
numbers, baby.

21:20.033 --> 21:23.367
